    <hasReference rdf:resource="http://example.org/ontology#R039"/>
    <hasManagementAdvice>Caution should be exercised before considering concurrent administration of these medicinal products. If co-administration is necessary, ciclosporin levels should be monitored</hasManagementAdvice>
