    <hasSideEffectDescription>Myocarditis is inflammation of the heart muscle, or myocardium. This inflammation weakens your heart muscle, making it harder for your heart to pump. This can be caused by viral infections or inflammatory conditions.</hasSideEffectDescription>
  </rdf:Description>
