    <hasSideEffectDescription>Metabolic acidosis is a condition in which acids build up in your body. Causes include untreated diabetes, the loss of bicarbonate in your body and kidney conditions. Symptoms include an accelerated heartbeat, confusion and fatigue.</hasSideEffectDescription>
